{"word":"ὑλώδης","slug":"ὑλώδης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑλώδης</b></el> <el>(ὑλ-ώδης, ες) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἶδος'><el>εἶδος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>woody, wooded</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>τὰ ὑλώδη</el> <i>wooded ground</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>turbid, muddy</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}